definition.value: An organic heterohexacyclic compound that is the major chromenoxanthone pigment present in Garcinia morella Desr.seed coat extract.
A phenothiazine substituted on the nitrogen by a 3-(morpholin-4-yl)propanoyl group, and at position 2 by an (ethoxycarbonyl)amino group.

A pentacyclic triterpenoid that is 9beta,19-cyclolanostane substituted by an oxo group at position 3 and hydroxy groups at positions 7, 23R*, 24R* and 25. It has been isolated from the leaves of Combretum quadrangulare.
